    "v1": "On what has now been sown Thy blessing, Lord, bestow; The pow&#39;r is Thine alone To make it spring and grow. Do Thou in grace the harvest raise, And Thou alone shalt have the praise.",
    "v2": "To Thee our wants are known, From Thee are all our pow&#39;rs; Accept what is Thine own And pardon what is ours. Our praises, Lord, and prayers receive And to Thy Word a blessing give.",
    "v3": "Oh, grant that each of us Now met before Thee here May meet together thus When Thou and Thine appear And follow Thee to Heav&#39;n, our home. E&#39;en so, Amen, Lord Jesus, come!"
  },
